    "A similar approach was adopted for one-and two-year-ahead predictions.",
    "Figure 10 in the Appendix A illustrates the procedure.",
    "A summary of the hyperparameters across the six validation periods is provided in Appendix B.",
    "In the final stage of our analysis, we assess the performance of the various multivariate models using three distinct metrics: the absolute relative bias (ARB), the Dawid-Sebastiani score (DSS, Dawid and Sebastiani, 1999; Gneiting and Raftery, 2007) and the interval score (IS, Gneiting and Raftery, 2007).",
